this area and wait me there"

"So"thought Orchestra "Vamprah is here..."

Orchestra remembered all Advices that Blacknightmare had given him 
about Vamprah, his thoughts were interrupted when Wheeljack started 
to walke towards the lab.

"Come" said Wheeljack"I'll give tou the spark-container"
